<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08294</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT UPGRADING THE SALARIES OF EMPLOYEES OF THE COMMISSION ON ELECTIONS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Proposes to increase the salary grades of field COMELEC employees such as Contested Ballot Box Custodians; Election Assistants; Election Officers and Field Officers (within and outside the NCR); Election Precincts Analysts; Regional Election Attorney; and Provincial Elections Supervisors.

Aims to reclassifies and upgrades all remaining rank and file plantilla positions in the main and field offices, including casual employees.

